original: Högberg, Erik, tandläkare, Västervik, f. 12/3/89 i Jönköp. av brygg :äg. Anders Gustaf H. o. Anna Christina Andersdotter. G. 15 m. Anna Wig-sten. Biarn: Birgit f. 17, Vera 19, Else 20. — Stud:ex. i Jönköp. 09, tiandil:-kand. H, tandliäk. 14. Prakt, tandläkare i Västervik 14-43. Hobby: musik.
translated: Högberg, Erik, dentist, from Västervik, born March 12, 1889 in Jönköping to dock owner Anders Gustaf H. and Anna Christina Andersdotter. Married on the 15th of an unspecified month to Anna Wigsten. Children: Birgit born 1917, Vera born 1919, and Else born 1920. He graduated high school in Jönköping in 1909, and graduated with a degree in dentistry in 1914. He practiced dentistry in Västervik from 1914-1943. His hobby was music.

article.name: Erik Högberg, A Passionate Dentist and Musician
